Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的中继殖民地还有3个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已全部压制 未引起混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说总共5个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 真是不可原谅的疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也很高明 但看来我们也太过关注地面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们都集中到月球轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处分稍后再作打算
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus基地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按您的指示 已安排罗兰队前往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么可以让Minerva和月球舰队休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们连续作战应该都累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球舰队如此 Minerva更是出色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多亏他们或许真能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有报告说这次终于铲除了再次逃亡的吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有情报说大西洋联邦总统还在Arzachel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已无法控制军队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们也真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心存侥幸的安逸心理将会招致巨大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该早就充分认识到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次又未能防范于未然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 并不是在责备你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不得不谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向牺牲的众多生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但想到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要创造出绝不会再重演这种惨剧的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为对逝去的人们最低限度的补偿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得能休息了 为什么突然进行射击训练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经睡过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷说要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候太仓促
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰和梅琳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想说的 只是要你别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想到他们可能还活着 我也无法保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是真没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也知道那是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且无法排除嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想叫你别介意 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入角度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通路正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel进入8号地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Archangel 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入8号地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:54.75,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,月面都市 哥白尼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那打败我的Impulse驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是那个叫真的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在驾驶Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那时候说实话真吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会被真干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时我也在犹豫是否该和ZAFT作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉也在 总想尽力逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel也被打中 真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 或许正因此而明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长和雷的棘手之处就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交谈起来确实觉得他们说的都对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我明白 实际上也是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真也…恐怕无法脱离这点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他也是个为梦想努力的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要被她的形象所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你暂时藏身起来较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会亏待你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那全都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个人 是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就算你也无法一直这样做下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 你迟早也会被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能 这种事…绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了 请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长还没有任何消息?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没办法 现在PLANT确实出了大事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这拉克丝小姐也很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在确实形势复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这哥白尼也是 据说Archangel刚刚入港呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候登上月球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是不是也一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是 在奥布说自己和Archangel一起的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很伤脑筋呢 那个人也真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样议长的努力都白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐其实并不是那种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐总是热爱和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在需要的时候总会引导我们 身先士卒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才会跟随她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的拉克丝小姐 就是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为自从开战以来 一直在议长身边努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正的拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我莎拉 拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会协助您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不这样大家都会困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会想出好主意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很久没有外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经在舰内过了几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 前不久一直在宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再往前是海底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明白这是事出无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但难免有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走了 拉米亚斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗 只让他们去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 只是去市内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保镖也很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这事 是说你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想出去呼吸新鲜空气的话我很乐意奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在船里也不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,责任又那么重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那总之先从舰内护卫做起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起…去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不是同一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次来哥白尼 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么生气 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 拉克丝她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和拉克丝都是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用再一个人拼命了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我觉得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是米亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命 我会被杀 拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一感觉 像是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但也不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 利用这点设计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  米亚·坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是议长的拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你保护拉克丝马上回船上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我找增援 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 别说傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她呼唤的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天必须这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 总之先和船上联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的阿斯兰 我也知道是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有大家在 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用 不过要当心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰? 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个傻瓜 说了把他引到舞台上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信息我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也知道是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是最后的机会 米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信上写着求救 不然会被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐其实并不是那种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的拉克丝小姐 就是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福世界真的得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和国民也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点绝不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音和脸都一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克丝 有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚 够了 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想得到名字的话让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有模样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此 你和我也是不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谁都无法成为自己以外的任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 正因如此才有你我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 能够邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他人 甚至和自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的梦想是你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请为此而歌唱 为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想不能为他人所用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少人 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 是莎拉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 穆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快保护拉克丝她们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的一直给你添麻烦 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚 米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:21:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的歌…和生命 请千万别忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽朗温柔的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点想和大家再见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点送她到Archangel 穆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下的只有一张照片和碟片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法欺骗的生命与思念的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变的事是梦吗 无法改变的自己是真实的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝愁云不展的眼眸正朝向最大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对恶梦的世界 Freedom
